{
  "stem": "10768.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My brother, my cousin, and myself, without that [INAUDIBLE] without the gentlemen who kept with us, were left in the middle of the road with whatever we had on our body.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, the end of November, beginning of December in Russia-- and this was already from-- this was Taganrog, near Rostov.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were going more east.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the trend was not to go, let's say, where the front was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The trend was to go more south, because the temperature was a little bit-- was a little bit warmer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't have winter clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the trains were not running.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If there was a passenger train, it was re-taken by the soldiers, who were also running from their military unit.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "God knows where?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was the biggest chaos one can imagine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the, big-- the train where-- the other trains, not the personal trains, but the cattle trains, were filled with wood, or whatever the Russians wanted to move away deep into Russia-- not to leave it to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If there were fields with, with, grain, they burned it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If there were woods or wood that they couldn't take away, they burned it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't want it should fall into the German hands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we really had to wait on a station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On a station, you couldn't buy anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing was available.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only thing-- if it was a more influential Russian dignitary who was with his wife and a child, and he had two, three valises and we helped him to carry from one train to be other, or helped him with something, he'd throw us a crumb.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were able to sort of survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had no money what to buy for.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
